o when I saw this positive pregnancy test I have to admit, at the time, I wasn't jumping for joy.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this positive pregnancy test\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was full of fear because that's all I have known.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as the weeks kept going by it was hard to wipe the smile off our faces.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weeks\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the smile\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"our faces\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser thatsupports HTML5 video Up Next 'To the little one we never thought we'd meet, we can not wait to hold you in our arms.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.31441951667815e-18, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7072676445246437e-16, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this video\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"a web browser\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"the little one\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"our arms\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You were worth every tear, every setback, and every prayer.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To all the people who supported us through the darkest days, thank you.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"the darkest days\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I would not have made it to this point without the strength of my family and friends who managed to hold me up when I was falling apart.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"the strength\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: 'It is also incredibly important for me to recognise that although this is the best news in the world for Thomas and I, my heart aches for anyone that sees this and feels pain.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9999999754104468, \"rank\": 2.456112896521765e-08, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best news\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was so hard for me to write this because it feels like I am caught between two worlds.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two worlds\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not an easy road and I would not wish it upon my worst enemy.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an easy road\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"my worst enemy\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one hell of an emotional roller coaster.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one hell\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional roller coaster\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay strong, keep fighting, but most importantly do not forget to be kind to yourself.'\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympia, best known for her role as Paige Smith in Australian soap Neighbours,opened up about miscarrying twins in an emotional message last year.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999995422050372, \"rank\": 4.5779518533490755e-07, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}, {\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paige Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9977427691090246, \"rank\": 0.0012669219374793518, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2041, \"title\"